SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

		    ifnull(TABLE_ROWS, '0') as TABLE_ROWS,\
		    ifnull(DATA_LENGTH, '0') as DATA_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(INDEX_LENGTH, '0') as INDEX_LENGTH,\
		    ifnull(DATA_FREE, '0') as DATA_FREE,\

		  FROM information_schema.tables\
		  WHERE TABLE_SCHEMA = 'sys'

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\

	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\

	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250

SELECT\
	    ifnull(SCHEMA_NAME, 'NONE') as SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    DIGEST,\
	    LEFT(DIGEST_TEXT, 120) as DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    COUNT_STAR,\
	    SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    SUM_ERRORS,\
	    SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  FROM (\
	    SELECT *\
	    FROM performance_schema.events_statements_summary_by_digest\
	    WHERE SCHEMA_NAME NOT IN ('mysql', 'performance_schema', 'information_schema')\
	      AND LAST_SEEN > DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 86400 SECOND)\
	    ORDER BY LAST_SEEN DESC\
	  )Q\
	  GROUP BY\
	    Q.SCHEMA_NAME,\
	    Q.DIGEST,\
	    Q.DIGEST_TEXT,\
	    Q.COUNT_STAR,\
	    Q.SUM_TIMER_WAIT,\
	    Q.SUM_ERRORS,\
	    Q.SUM_WARNINGS,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_AFFECTED,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_SENT,\
	    Q.SUM_ROWS_EXAMINED,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_DISK_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_CREATED_TMP_TABLES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_MERGE_PASSES,\
	    Q.SUM_SORT_ROWS,\
	    Q.SUM_NO_INDEX_USED\
	  ORDER BY SUM_TIMER_WAIT DESC\
	  LIMIT 250
